Hatta said. Power companies should make the opaque transmission fees=20
transparent and set them accordingly with regional demand, he said.=20
Yoshinori Omuro, vice president of Takashimaya Co.'s (J.TKA or 8233)=20
management department, acknowledged the slow progress of the deregulation.=20
